as click, tap, pinch, and swipe—to zoom in on documents, browse through music or webpages, rotate photos, open Notification Center, and more.</p><div id=\"mchlf8620178\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Trackpad gestures</h2><p>Use one or more fingers on the surface of your trackpad to click, tap, slide, swipe, and more. For example, to move between pages of a document, swipe left or right with two fingers. To see all of the trackpad gestures you can use with your Mac, or to turn off or customize gestures, choose Apple menu <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/e043ddf1a45711e13f0b30612db65e21.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"26\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_AppleLogo.png\"> &gt; System Preferences, then click Trackpad.</p><p><a href=\"x-help-action://openPrefPane?bundleId=com.apple.preference.trackpad\" class=\"URL\">Open Trackpad preferences for me</a></p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/36c9770a55b5fb8c1f97855d196753e8.png\" alt=\"Examples of trackpad gestures for zooming in and out of a webpage and moving between full-screen apps.\" height=\"288\" width=\"400\" originalImageName=\"Art/S0240_GesturesOverviewTrackpad.png\"></figure></div><div id=\"mchl9eb93fbc\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Mouse gestures</h2><p>Use one or more fingers on the surface of your mouse to click, tap, slide, or swipe items. For example, to move between pages of a document, swipe left or right with one finger. To see all of the mouse gestures you can use with your Mac, or to turn off or customize gestures, choose Apple menu <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/e043ddf1a45711e13f0b30612db65e21.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"26\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_AppleLogo.png\"> &gt; System Preferences, then click Mouse.</p><p><a href=\"x-help-action://openPrefPane?bundleId=com.apple.preference.mouse\" class=\"URL\">Open Mouse preferences for me</a></p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/681fca1ef0b34c50a0022ff6f96e9bda.png\" alt=\"Examples of mouse gestures for zooming in and out of a webpage and moving between full-screen apps.\" height=\"300\" width=\"466\" originalImageName=\"Art/S0241_GesturesOverviewMouse.png\"></figure></div><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-mouse-preferences&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH29222&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change Mouse preferences on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-your-mouses-response-speed&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLP1138&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change mouse tracking, double-click, and scrolling speed on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-trackpad-preferences&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLP1226&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change Trackpad preferences on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/HT204895\" class=\"URL\">Apple Support article: Use Multi-Touch gestures on your Mac</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["DisplayVersion/macOS Mojave 10.14","IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","ContentMode/liveContent","ArchivalStatus/Unarchived","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexON","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"S